reviews.text:
A local style restaurant. Good for your late dinner. It closes 12:00 midnight.

Foods were ok, not that special, not that bad, not that impressive.

Staffs are average nice, and the hall was ok.
Not much parking but the tai wai mtr station is just across the street

At a convenient location,  service is fairly good.

Good for drivers , you can see your car if you park outside.

Price is average,  food average.

Cleaniness sometimes is a bit of concern.
Affordable and delicious meals
very bad...special the service
